  "text": "Global coexpression analysis reveals most metGSL biosynthesis genes in Arabidopsis. Network map of a typical coexpression module involved in metGSL biosynthesis. Nodes in the map represent genes, and edges connecting two genes represent the weight (transformed MR score) for the association. The map was drawn using a Fruchterman-Reingold force-directed layout with the igraph R package (http:// igraph.org). (Reprinted from [CITATION_1] , Figure 3A. ",
